operations and maintenance
requirements and design parameters.

37
00:02:10,263 --> 00:02:12,428
These were settling
and thickening tanks,

38
00:02:12,628 --> 00:02:15,581
unplanted drying beds,
planted drying beds,

39
00:02:15,781 --> 00:02:19,603
co-composting,
cotreatment with waste water

40
00:02:19,803 --> 00:02:22,267
and effluent treatment technologies.

41
